# Maxwell material library — GO_Steel_IEC_M111_30P
# Description: Hi-B non-domain-refined 0.30mm (IEC M111-30P typical values)
# IEC grade: M111-30P
# Thickness: 0.3 mm
# DATA TYPE: REPRESENTATIVE TYPICAL VALUES (not manufacturer-guaranteed)
# Source: IEC 60404-8-7 grade specs + Nippon Steel catalog D008en
# Ref:  HI-B 0.30mm   μ_r@800A/m=1920 → B800≈1.929T (Nippon D008en App.III)
#       CGO 0.30mm    μ_r@800A/m=1820 → B800≈1.829T (Nippon D008en App.III)
# Verify all values against your material supplier before production use.
# Import: File > Import > Import Material Library (.amat)

$begin 'GO_Steel_IEC_M111_30P'
	'CoordinateSystemType'='Cartesian'
	'BulkOrSurface'='Bulk'
	$begin 'PhysicsTypes'
		'set'('Electromagnetic')
	$end 'PhysicsTypes'
	$begin 'AttachedData'
	$end 'AttachedData'
	$begin 'ModifierData'
